      "text": "🎧 【Harmonica Solo】 🎧\nNavy Lark (Version 2) by James Moody\nHarmonica: Timothy Yip\nPiano: Alison Ma\n今個星期同大家分享另一首口琴小品Navy Lark (Version 2)🛥️ Version 2同上一個錄音Version 1係有唔同架🎶 接下來數個星期繼續為大家分享不同口琴音樂🌟\nStay tuned for the next piece👀\n#recording #harmonica #口琴 #timothyyip #music\nhttps://www.facebook.com/reel/999351019358521/",
