      "text": "We are incredibly proud to officially welcome Japanese chromatic harmonica player and educator Rei Yamashita to the Hohner Family! 🇯🇵✨\nKnown for her crystal-clear tone and deeply expressive musical style, Rei bridges genres seamlessly from timeless classical masterpieces to contemporary popular music. Beyond her brilliant performances, her dedication to teaching through workshops and lessons is inspiring the next generation of players. 🎶\nRei has trusted Hohner for many years and we are honored by her words on this new chapter:\n„Hohner instruments offer a rich and beautiful tone with\noutstanding expressive possibilities... For me, Hohner is a very special brand that continues to expand the possibilities of the chromatic harmonica. Through my performances and educational activities, I hope to share the beauty of harmonica music from Japan with audiences around the world together with Hohner.“ ❤️\nWe are thrilled to embark on this journey together to share the magic of the chromatic harmonica worldwide. 🤝🌍",
